{"title": "Comte de Monte-Cristo", "description": "Edmond Dant\u00e8s, a young seaman with a promising future, is arrested at his wedding ceremony under calomnious charges, and locked up in the Chateau d'If for 14 years. During this time, he secretly meets another detainee, l'Abb\u00e9 Faria, an erudite believed to be insane, who becomes his friend and teacher, and who, upon his death, gives Edmond the secret to a hidden treasure.<br /><br />Dant\u00e8s then manages to escape, almost drowning in the process, and is believed by all to be dead. With the knowledge and the treasure transmitted by l'abb\u00e9 Faria, and his own wish for revenge, Edmond Dant\u00e8s plots the downfall of his enemies under the identity of the Count of Monte-Cristo.<br /><br />Summary by Jc Guan.", "duration": 185195, "language": "French", "authors": [{"id": "431", "name": "Alexandre Dumas"}], "coverArt": "http://www.archive.org/download/librivox_cd_covers/monte_cristo.jpg", "copyright_year": "1844", "genres": ["Action & Adventure Fiction", "Romance"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "LibriVox Volunteers"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "Jc Guan"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Gesine"}], "sections": [{"section": 1, "title": "Marseille \u2013 L\u2019arriv\u00e9e", "readers": [1474], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/comte_monte_cristo_jg_librivox/montecristo_001_dumas_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1108}, {"section": 2, "title": "Le p\u00e8re et le fils", "readers": [1474], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/comte_monte_cristo_jg_librivox/montecristo_002_dumas_64kb.mp3", "duration": 890}, {"section": 3, "title": "Les Catalans", "readers": [1474], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/comte_monte_cristo_jg_librivox/montecristo_003_dumas_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1464}, {"section": 4, "title": "Complot", "readers": [1474], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/comte_monte_cristo_jg_librivox/montecristo_004_dumas_64kb.mp3", "duration": 913}, {"section": 5, "tit